Heat 86-83 to tie the National Basketball Association Finals at
two games apiece.  The teams will return to the American Airlines Center in
Dallas for Game 5 on June 9 before the best-of-seven series
returns to Miami.  The Heat beat the Mavericks in six games in each teamâ€™s
